their tricks.

41:08.635 --> 41:10.137
Sounds like a win to me.

41:10.172 --> 41:11.032
No, no.

41:11.068 --> 41:12.841
Come here, look at the files.

41:19.179 --> 41:21.646
Each woman gives the same
street as their address.

41:21.681 --> 41:22.780
The same development.

41:22.815 --> 41:24.419
All owned by Garrett Field.

41:24.454 --> 41:26.421
Okay, so I'm not following.

41:26.456 --> 41:28.418
Well, maybe you're right.

41:28.453 --> 41:31.726
Maybe they all just found
different forms of occupation.

41:31.761 --> 41:34.124
Or, maybe whoever
they're working for

41:34.160 --> 41:36.624
just got a little bit better
at hiding it.

41:37.160 --> 41:38.201
WOMAN AT PARTY:
Go high, boys.

41:39.036 --> 41:40.162
Piece.

41:40.197 --> 41:42.765
MAN AT PARTY:

42:36.185 --> 42:37.153
MAN 1:
Where are we going?

42:37.188 --> 42:38.162
